<p>Teigen and her husband John Legend listed their Beverly Hills home in August for $24 million.</p>

<p>The couple purchased the home, which was previously owned by Rihanna, in January 2016 for $14.1 million.</p>

<p>The 8,520-square-foot three-story home boasts 5 bedrooms, 8 bathrooms, sitting on a .86-acre parcel of land.</p>

